latestIgtvVideos.title: We love you, Maa! ❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Zindagi ke safar me raahi, milte hain bichad jaane ko aur de jaate hain yaadein tanhai me tadpaane ko. @vinita.dutt.96 ❤️
@kunaldutt15 
I remember whenever I made such videos for you or Kunal, you’d get so excited and watch them a gazillion times, on repeat. Now we’re watching this video on loop but can’t stop ourselves from crying. This video is absolutely beautiful yet heartbreaking. 
Thank you Megha didi for this❤️
We miss you, Maa! 
Hope you’re still stalking me❤️

My mother has taught me how to love unconditionally, how to give out to the world more than you receive and how to be strong enough to deal with anything with a smile. This woman has been and will always be my strength. ♥️
No matter where I go or what I do, I know she’ll always be my biggest supporter. 
Forever trying to look like her. ♥️ I love you, Maa. 
Chalo thori aur photos click karwaein? I miss you. @vinita.dutt.96
